title: Digital Printed Wooden Wall Clock ? 12x16 Inch Decorative Hanging Clock Without Battery
description:
Elevate your interior with this beautifully crafted Digital Printed Wooden Wall Clock, designed to blend art and functionality. Measuring 12x16 inches, this wall-mounted timepiece showcases a rich floral print on a dark blue background, adding a touch of nature-inspired elegance to any room.

Made from durable wood, the clock features white numerals and yellow hands that stand out clearly against the vibrant backdrop. Its battery-free design offers a hassle-free experience, and the hook-mounted setup ensures easy installation on any wall surface.

Perfect for living rooms, bedrooms, offices, or gift-giving, this decorative clock brings warmth, style, and practicality to your space. Whether you're refreshing your d?cor or looking for a unique accent piece, this clock is a standout choice.
